      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, turn the heat up to high</p><p>Add your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> with your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong>, stirring to dissolve</p><p>Add your <strong>smoked basa fillet[s]</strong>, and cook, covered, for 5 min or until the fish is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
